# 詞：睇怕

1. 天口咁陰沉，睇怕陣間會落大雨。 (The sky is so gloomy; it looks like it's going to rain heavily soon.)
2. 佢成日咳嗽，睇怕係感冒咗。 (He's been coughing all day; it seems like he has caught a cold.)
3. 咁多車塞住條路，睇怕我哋趕唔切搭飛機。 (There are so many cars blocking the road; I'm afraid we won't make it to catch the flight.)
4. 佢塊面咁青，睇怕身體唔舒服。 (His face looks so pale; it appears he isn't feeling well.)
5. 個項目咁複雜，睇怕要搞幾個月先搞得掂。 (This project is so complicated; it looks like it will take a few months to finish.)
6. 佢咁耐都冇覆訊息，睇怕係嬲咗我。 (He hasn't replied to my message for so long; I guess he's angry with me.)
7. 間屋咁殘舊，睇怕修起來要花好多錢。 (The house is so dilapidated; it seems like it will cost a lot of money to repair.)
8. 佢講嘢咁含糊，睇怕係想隱瞞啲嘢。 (He's speaking so vaguely; it looks like he's trying to hide something.)
9. 咁多人排隊，睇怕輪到我哋已經係夜晚啦。 (So many people are queuing; I'm afraid it'll be night by the time it's our turn.)
10. 佢最近成日遲到，睇怕份工保唔住。 (He's been late every day recently; it seems like he won't be able to keep his job.) [end of text]


